# Ugra LLM Layer

## Port pattern

```
Agents/Cognition → CompletionGateway → LLMCompletionPort → Provider Adapter
```

## Adding a provider

1. Implement `LLMCompletionPort` in `providers/`
2. Register in `factory.py`
3. Use httpx, not LangChain SDK in new code

## Forbidden

```python
# ❌ Business logic in prompts/LLM calls
prompt = "If match > 60, recommend applying..."

# ✅ Business logic in CognitionEngine
should_apply, rationale = cognition.evaluate_vacancy_fit(...)
```

## Config

`DEFAULT_LLM_PROVIDER` = openai | anthropic | ollama — switch without code changes.
